room_title: Escape room "AgXscape" by Hilmar Cheese Company Visitor Center in Modesto
room_description: You have always wondered what it is like have a farm. Now your team is managing Bob’s dairy. You get a call from a neighbor that there is a severe situation. You must quickly find the emergency instructions to unlock the vaccines to save the cows! These are dairy farm challenges you won’t experience unless you hang out with a dairy farmer. And, we are in a town with more cows than people.
